{
  "stem": "5654.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And every now and again, if we see apple in-- in the-- you see a big country.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was a lot of apple trees and pear trees.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to pinch them on the way, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the farmers used to wait for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometimes they used to shoot-- what do you call-- pellet, a salt pellet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you- if you'd get them into your-- into your skin, it did hurt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to be very careful that they didn't see us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was-- we would try to survive, of course, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- [BACKROUND NOISE] And the teachers at school?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Did they differentiate between you  and the local children?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I can remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, you see, in France it-- the schools are very strict.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, you know, you're not allowed to be taught religion at school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's a Napoleonic law.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So no religion was allowed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And although, we were strict-- for instance, in France, you don't go to school on Thursday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you must go on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Saturday, public schools are open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so, because we were not allowed to write on Shabbat, so the teacher had - had made on the date was-- recitation, is it?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or, resuscitation?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Recitations.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We used to learn about Moliere, La Fontaine, and all that sort of thing, you know, by heart.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE ]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- so they didn't made us-- they didn't have any, what you call, exams, so that we'd miss out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I must say, for this they were quite fair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they knew that we were religious, and we were not allowed to write.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was strictly lectures date on the-- on the Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a little bit, but not very much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not very much.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
